<bibRefCitation id="4A0A4B081A5F34739576063AFD71A23A" author="Yin, C. M. &amp; Peng, X. J. &amp; Gong, L. S. &amp; Kim, J. P." box="[312,653,1839,1866]" pageId="11" pageNumber="322" pagination="25 - 30" refId="ref9561" refString="Yin, C. M., Peng, X. J., Gong, L. S. &amp; Kim, J. P. (1997) Three new species of the genus Phrurolithus (Araneae: Liocranidae) from China. Korean Arachnology, 13 (1), 25 - 30." type="journal article" year="1997">Yin, Peng, Gong &amp; Kim, 1997</bibRefCitation>
